@startuml
!include ../style.puml

participant "Client" as Client
participant "Node A\n(Coordinator)" as Coord
participant "Node B\n(Participant)" as Part

note over Coord
  **Coordinator Role**
  Maintains the ""TxnRecord"" 
  in memory for the lifetime 
  of the transaction.
end note

note over Part
  **Participant Role**
  Maintains the actual data 
  and provisional intents.
end note

'[step]
Client -> Coord: BeginTransaction(txnId=1)
Coord -> Coord: Create TxnRecord(status=PENDING)
Coord --> Client: OK

'[step]
Client -> Part: TxnWriteRequest(key="X", val="v2")
Part -> Part: Write Intent("X" -> "v2")
Part --> Client: OK
@enduml
